<event name="RADIKAL_WARP">
	<text>Name: RadiKal Sector
	Type: Neutral
	Dominant Faction: RK Bam, RK Punk, RK Scorch
	Rebel Threat Level: Very Low
	Locations of Interest: RK Labs, Scorch BIL, Pirate Trinity, Hideout
	
	The [style[color:ff3377]]dangerous[[/style]] sector where RadiKal subfactions develop illegal equipment. Specialists from everywhere secretly come to keep up with the tech, regulate its trade or steal it. Mind whatever Radikal (RK) equipment you have in there!
	[Feedback? @Dj0z on discord.]</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Exit hyperspeed.</text>
		<event load="START_RADIKAL"/>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="COORDS" blue="false">
		<text>Reroute.</text>
		<event load="REROUTE_MENU"/>
	</choice>
</event>
<!-- REF: Darkest Desire v4.1.4 for MV v5.5.1
<event name="DEEPONE_WARP">
	<text>Name: Deep One Territory
	Type: Neutral
	Unique: False
	Dominant Faction: The Deep Ones
	Rebel Threat Level: Medium-Low
	
	Not much is known about the secretive Deep Ones, they simply one day arose from Old Earth's oceans within a fleet of spaceships and took to the stars; their existence prior allegedly unknown to the humans who dwelled on the surface. They're a hot-headed race that often suffers when it comes to communicating to outsiders, but there's no bad blood between them and the Federation. The same can't be said about the Theocracy, however, who finds the Deep One's religious beliefs to be heinously blasphemous.</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Exit hyperspeed.</text>
		<event load="START_DEEPONE"/>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="COORDS" blue="false">
		<text>Reroute.</text>
		<event load="REROUTE_MENU"/>
	</choice>
</event> 
-->
